        lines {
          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "Sofia needs structured behavioral and cognitive intervention before the final exam. Her mathematical anxiety is amplifying minor gaps into full performance blocks, as seen in her 55% score on the Geometry Midterm."
