    modified_response: "I will write `/src/components/RAGWorkspace.tsx` containing the primary RAG Sessions left listing, the \"New Analysis\" creation workflow modal, and our high-fidelity Chatbot. The chatbot supports real-time text input with suggested prompt chips, a loading skeleton, and pure clean SVG visualizer panels (for Scores comparative ranking bar charts, grade trajectories timelines, unit competency heatmaps, and stats cards). It also manages our system-wide distraction-free \"Focus Mode\" toggles."
